Hinjewadi is located towards the west of Pune and is 21 kilometres from the Railway station. Over a period of time, it has developed into one of the biggest industrial areas of Pune, transforming from a sleepy village to a bustling neighbourhood. Hinjewadi is also home to historical attractions such as Shaniwar Wada, Vishrambaug Wada and Aga Khan Palace. The pride of Hinjewadi is its state of the art 500-acre Rajiv Gandhi Infotech Park which hosts a cluster of IT/ITES and BPO units. It houses some of India's largest IT conglomerates like Wipro, Tech Mahindra, TCS, Infosys, IBM and Cognizant. Hinjewadi is being developed in multiple phases. Phase 1, 2 and 3 are completed and further development has been planned from phase 4 onwards. Due to rapid development in the area, Hinjewadi faces heavy traffic congestion during peak hours. Man One Park Avenue - 1 bhk, 2 bhk and 3 bhk  at Ghodbunder Road, Thane West is a landmark residential project offering lavish yet thoughtfully designed residences. Man One Park Avenue Thane West is driven by passion and conceived by top class designers, and thus boasts of a fine blend of simple functionality and smart aesthetics. The project boasts of 30 plus acres of green zone and open space attached to the property. it aims to establish a new standard of excellence in residential living, and thus focuses on rejuvenating lives. The 90% of open space allows homebuyers to enjoy the magnificent view of Thane. In fact, it is the only project in the city that has 10 acres of free space and 32 acres of botanical garden.  What are the key details of this project?  You can choose from Man One Park Avenue 1 BHK and 2 BHK apartments. This is a mid stage project. There are 6 towers with 153 units in total.  What are the amenities on offer here?  There are a number of Man One Park Avenue amenities on offer for its residents, including a well-equipped gymnasium, swimming pool, sports facility, indoor games, multipurpose hall, landscaped gardens, cricket pitch, aerobics/yoga, club house, spa, senior citizen area, party area with lawn, cycling/jogging track, foot massage park, library, etc.  What are my locational benefits here?  The Man One Park Avenue location promises several advantages to the investors and buyers. Situated in the affluent vicinity of Hiranandani Estates, Patlipada, this project is only 15 minutes from Thane Station, while Powai can be reached in just 20 minutes. This project allows easy accessibility to major destinations such as Andheri/Lokhandwala, Fort (via Freeway), and so on. A number of business hubs are also well-connected to the project, including Bandra Kurla Complex, Vashi and Mindspace IT Park, Mhape, amongst others. The Eastern Express and the Western Express Highway are just 15 minutes drive away, while the Santacruz Airport can be reached in 35 minutes via SCLR.
